These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, indian, colombian, french
4 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, pony, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the russian##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the french is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
7. the indian is somewhere between the russian and the owner of the horse##7
8. the indian and the owner of the hedgehog have the same parity positions##9
9. the colombian and the owner of the turtle have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | russian | indian | colombian     | french |
| Pet           | pony   | hedgehog     | horse | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, fishing, camping, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person drinking lemonade have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
8. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | soy-milk    | 7up | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | video-games | fishing | camping      | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, 7up, juice
There 4 different types of food: potato, raspberry, peach, kiwi
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
2. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating potato##1
7. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
8. the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating raspberry have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | 7up   | sprite    | juice  |
| Food       | raspberry | kiwi | potato | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, social-worker, engineer, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, folk, jazz, soul
1. the fan gospel is the social-worker##1
2. the fan folk is on the right of the fan jazz##1
3. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
4. the fan soul is on the left or right of the engineer##3
5. the fan folk is on the left of the photographer##1
6. the accountant and the fan soul have the same parity positions##9
7. the engineer is on the left or right of the photographer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | accountant | engineer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | jazz             | folk          | soul | gospel    |

