2. the owner of the rat and the fan electronic have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the horse and the fan funk have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan reggae##1
6. the fan funk is not the owner of the horse##6
7. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan electronic##1
9. the owner of the turtle is not the fan reggae##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | jazz | reggae  | funk |
| Pet           | horse   | rat     | chinchilla | turtle      |

