4. the italian and the person watching fantasy movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching martial-arts movies and the italian have different parity positions##9
6. the spanish is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
7. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
8. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the egyptian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
