3. the person who's sport is cricket and the fan house have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the fan house is not to the right of the fan gospel##8
6. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
7. the fan house is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | country | house         | gospel     |
| Sport         | surfing | cricket  | handball | climbing |

