2. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is not the owner of the lizard##6
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles and the owner of the dog have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
