.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, onion, plum, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, roller, airplane, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
2. the person eating zucchini and the person driving the jet-ski have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
4. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
5. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person driving the jet-ski##7
6. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | plum | pineapple   | onion | zucchini |
| Transport   | airplane   | roller | bus    | jet-ski      |

