2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating orange##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating lime have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | blueberry | spinach | orange   | lime   |
| Hobby   | sudoku  | dancing   | filmmaking | baking |

