.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, kiwi, spinach, eggplant
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, dutch, nigerian
1. the person eating eggplant is not the nigerian##6
2. the nigerian is not to the right of the mexican##8
3. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the dutch##3
6. the nigerian is on the far left##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
8. the person eating mango is the argentine##1
9. the person eating eggplant and the mexican have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | kiwi   | eggplant    | spinach | mango    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | dutch   | argentine |

