5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person watching sports movies and the person drinking soy-milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching time-travel movies and the person drinking juice have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
