.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, iced-tea, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, indie, gospel, metal
 1. the person drinking water and the fan gospel have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 3. the fan punk is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##7
 4. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan gospel is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking coffee and the fan indie have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan metal##3
 9. the fan metal is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the fan punk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice  | coffee | iced-tea  | water |
| Music-Genre   | metal | gospel     | punk | indie     |

