1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta    | cola | iced-tea | 7up |
| Hobby      | writing | magic-tricks   | collecting   | sudoku   |

