.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, rock-climbing, dancing
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person drinking tea##6
 6. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is writing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 9. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is writing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | tea    | hot-chocolate        | sprite   | mirinda      |
| Hobby      | dancing | rock-climbing | writing | filmmaking |

 